00:01:29.058 --> 00:01:30.808
you go to the exact same angle,

00:01:30.808 --> 00:01:32.792
and then let go of its pumpkin.

00:01:32.792 --> 00:01:34.025
And this is gonna be a very useful video

00:01:34.025 --> 00:01:35.266
because you will find yourself

00:01:35.266 --> 00:01:39.463
